platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Plan a new metro in Chongqing

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Build the perfect commute on your next commute with the hypnotic Mini Metro. Strategy buffs and casual gamers alike will enjoy expanding a busy transit system by linking stations, directing trains, and upgrading lines. Theres a thrilling satisfaction in seeing subways come togetherand since no two games play alike, were always trying out new designs.
